- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as language modelling is a subfield of AI. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is a potential category as the paper mentions the storage and transmission of text data. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper discusses a novel measurement and the establishment of a comprehensive candidate lexicon.
